{"article_id":"ksaZcY0WUGk7F9ob","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"We now know","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"that Donald Trump Jr. , during the presidential campaign , met with a Russian lawyer","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"offering information","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"that was \" part of Russia and its government ' s support for Mr. Trump. \"","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"And we now know","depth":5},{"id":5,"text":"that the president ' s eldest son was less-than-forthcoming in his previous statements on the issue .","depth":5},{"id":6,"text":"When he tweeted images of the email chain about that June 9 , 2016 , meeting ,","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"he said","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"it was \" in order to be totally transparent. \"","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"But that transparency came days after a misleading statement about the meeting","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"and just as The New York Times was preparing to publish the emails .","depth":6},{"id":11,"text":"On July 8 , The New York Times broke the story","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"that Donald Trump Jr. had arranged a meeting at Trump Tower with a Russian lawyer , Natalia Veselnitskaya ,","depth":10},{"id":13,"text":"\" who has connections to the Kremlin. \"","depth":10},{"id":14,"text":"The president ' s son-in-law and now senior adviser , Jared Kushner , and Paul Manafort , then-campaign convention manager , also attended .","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"Here ' s what Trump Jr. told the Times about that meeting in a statement :","depth":10},{"id":16,"text":"Donald Trump Jr. , July 8 statement :","depth":11},{"id":17,"text":"`` It was a short introductory meeting .","depth":13},{"id":18,"text":"I asked Jared and Paul to stop by .","depth":14},{"id":19,"text":"We primarily discussed a program about the adoption of Russian children","depth":15},{"id":20,"text":"that was active and popular with American families years ago","depth":17},{"id":21,"text":"and was since ended by the Russian government ,","depth":17},{"id":22,"text":"but it was not a campaign issue at the time","depth":17},{"id":23,"text":"and there was no follow up .","depth":17},{"id":24,"text":"I was asked to attend the meeting by an acquaintance ,","depth":13},{"id":25,"text":"but was not told the name of the person","depth":14},{"id":26,"text":"I would be meeting with beforehand . ''","depth":14},{"id":27,"text":"But that was misleading","depth":10},{"id":28,"text":"and glossed over the reason for the meeting ,","depth":11},{"id":29,"text":"which the Times would soon report","depth":12},{"id":30,"text":"and Trump Jr. would acknowledge .","depth":12},{"id":31,"text":"On July 9 , the Times reported","depth":11},{"id":32,"text":"that Trump Jr. was \" promised damaging information about Hillary Clinton","depth":12},{"id":33,"text":"before agreeing to meet with a Kremlin-connected Russian lawyer during the 2016 campaign. \"","depth":12},{"id":34,"text":"His statement that day :","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"Trump Jr. , July 9 statement :","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"`` [ T ] he woman stated","depth":13},{"id":37,"text":"that she had information","depth":14},{"id":38,"text":"that individuals","depth":16},{"id":39,"text":"connected to Russia","depth":16},{"id":40,"text":"were funding the Democratic National Committee","depth":16},{"id":41,"text":"and supporting Mrs. Clinton .","depth":16},{"id":42,"text":"Her statements were vague , ambiguous","depth":15},{"id":43,"text":"and made no sense .","depth":15},{"id":44,"text":"No details or supporting information was provided or even offered .","depth":14},{"id":45,"text":"It quickly became clear that she had no meaningful information .","depth":13},{"id":46,"text":"She then changed subjects","depth":13},{"id":47,"text":"and began discussing the adoption of Russian children","depth":14},{"id":48,"text":"and mentioned the Magnitsky Act .","depth":14},{"id":49,"text":"It became clear to me","depth":13},{"id":50,"text":"that this was the true agenda all along","depth":14},{"id":51,"text":"and that the claims of potentially helpful information were a pretext for the meeting . ''","depth":14},{"id":52,"text":"And by July 11 , through the Times ' reporting and Trump Jr. ' s own release of the emails , we knew","depth":7},{"id":53,"text":"that the meeting was explicitly about potential dirt on the soon-to-be Democratic presidential nominee from a purported \" Russian government attorney . \"","depth":7},{"id":54,"text":"The June 3 , 2016 , email from music publicist Rob Goldstone said","depth":8},{"id":55,"text":"that Russian pop star Emin Agalarov had asked Goldstone to contact Trump Jr. on behalf of his father , Aras Agalarov , a Russian real estate developer","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"who has ties to Donald Trump Sr. ,","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"including his 2013 Miss Universe pageant in Moscow .","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"\" The Crown prosecutor of Russia met with his father Aras this morning","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"and in their meeting offered to provide the Trump campaign with some official documents and information","depth":11},{"id":60,"text":"that would incriminate Hillary and her dealings with Russia","depth":12},{"id":61,"text":"and would be very useful to your father , \"","depth":12},{"id":62,"text":"Goldstone wrote .","depth":9},{"id":63,"text":"\" This is obviously very high level and sensitive information","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"but is part of Russia and its government ' s support for Mr. Trump","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"- helped along by Aras and Emin . \"","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"Trump Jr. responded 17 minutes later ,","depth":7},{"id":67,"text":"saying","depth":8},{"id":68,"text":"that \" if it ' s what you say","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"I love it. \"","depth":9},{"id":70,"text":"Four days later , Goldstone emailed again","depth":5},{"id":71,"text":"to \" schedule a meeting with you and The Russian government attorney","depth":6},{"id":72,"text":"who is flying over from Moscow . \"","depth":6},{"id":73,"text":"Trump Jr. ' s statements on the meeting evolved","depth":7},{"id":74,"text":"as the Times gathered more information .","depth":7},{"id":75,"text":"He first said only","depth":8},{"id":76,"text":"that the meeting was \" primarily \" about the adoption of Russian children ,","depth":8},{"id":77,"text":"but he later acknowledged","depth":8},{"id":78,"text":"he had agreed to a meeting","depth":9},{"id":79,"text":"promising damaging information about Clinton from ,","depth":11},{"id":80,"text":"the emails say ,","depth":11},{"id":81,"text":"a \" Russian government attorney . \"","depth":10},{"id":82,"text":"This wasn ' t the first time","depth":8},{"id":83,"text":"the newspaper had asked Trump Jr. about meetings with Russians .","depth":8},{"id":84,"text":"In its July 8 story , The New York Times noted","depth":10},{"id":85,"text":"that in an interview with the younger Trump back in March , he said","depth":12},{"id":86,"text":"he had never \" set up \" any meetings with Russians and \" certainly none","depth":13},{"id":87,"text":"that I was representing the campaign in any way , shape or form. \"","depth":13},{"id":88,"text":"Further , he denied","depth":12},{"id":89,"text":"that he ever discussed government policies","depth":14},{"id":90,"text":"related to Russia","depth":14},{"id":91,"text":"with any Russians .","depth":13},{"id":92,"text":"None of that is accurate .","depth":9},{"id":93,"text":"The New York Times , July 8 :","depth":9},{"id":94,"text":"`` Donald Trump Jr. had denied participating in any campaign-related meetings with Russian nationals","depth":11},{"id":95,"text":"when he was interviewed by The Times in March .","depth":11},{"id":96,"text":"'Did I meet with people","depth":14},{"id":97,"text":"that were Russian ?","depth":14},{"id":98,"text":"I ' m sure ,","depth":15},{"id":99,"text":"I ' m sure","depth":15},{"id":100,"text":"I did , '","depth":14},{"id":101,"text":"he said .","depth":12},{"id":102,"text":"'But none","depth":14},{"id":103,"text":"that were set up .","depth":14},{"id":104,"text":"None","depth":15},{"id":105,"text":"that I can think of at the moment .","depth":15},{"id":106,"text":"And certainly none","depth":15},{"id":107,"text":"that I was representing the campaign in any way , shape or form . ' ``","depth":15},{"id":108,"text":"Asked at that time","depth":15},{"id":109,"text":"whether he had ever discussed government policies","depth":16},{"id":110,"text":"related to Russia ,","depth":16},{"id":111,"text":"the younger Mr. Trump replied ,","depth":14},{"id":112,"text":"' A hundred percent no . ' `","depth":13},{"id":113,"text":"` Let ' s start with Trump Jr. ' s assertion","depth":9},{"id":114,"text":"that he had never \" set up \" any meetings with Russians .","depth":9},{"id":115,"text":"Indeed , he did .","depth":9},{"id":116,"text":"The emails between Goldstone and Trump Jr. leave no question","depth":10},{"id":117,"text":"that this meeting was \" set up \" between Trump Jr. and what was purported to be a \" Russian government attorney. \"","depth":10},{"id":118,"text":"The face-to-face meeting subsequently occurred on June 9 , 2016 , in Trump Tower .","depth":8},{"id":119,"text":"In an interview on Fox News on July 11 , Trump Jr. said","depth":11},{"id":120,"text":"he may have met during the campaign with other Russians , but not in \" a formalized meeting . \"","depth":11},{"id":121,"text":"Trump Jr. , July 11 :","depth":11},{"id":122,"text":"`` You know ,","depth":13},{"id":123,"text":"I don ' t even know .","depth":13},{"id":124,"text":"I ' ve probably met with other people from Russia ...","depth":13},{"id":125,"text":"not in the context of actual - a formalized meeting or anything like that","depth":14},{"id":126,"text":"because why would I ? ''","depth":14},{"id":127,"text":"In his meeting with the Russian attorney in June 2016 , was Trump Jr. representing the campaign \" in any way , shape or form \" ?","depth":12},{"id":128,"text":"Clearly , he was .","depth":12},{"id":129,"text":"The primary purpose of the meeting ,","depth":13},{"id":130,"text":"according to Goldstone ' s initial email ,","depth":13},{"id":131,"text":"was \" to provide the Trump campaign with some official documents and information","depth":13},{"id":132,"text":"that would incriminate Hillary and her dealings with Russia","depth":14},{"id":133,"text":"and would be very useful to your father. \"","depth":14},{"id":134,"text":"Further , Trump Jr. later responded","depth":12},{"id":135,"text":"that in addition to himself , he would likely be joined by \" Paul Manafort","depth":14},{"id":136,"text":"( campaign boss ) \"","depth":14},{"id":137,"text":"and \" my brother-in-law. \"","depth":13},{"id":138,"text":"Manafort had been named campaign convention manager in March 2016","depth":12},{"id":139,"text":"and would be named campaign manager on June 20 .","depth":12},{"id":140,"text":"Finally , the emails and statements from Trump Jr. about the meeting contradict his claim","depth":6},{"id":141,"text":"that he never discussed government policies","depth":8},{"id":142,"text":"related to Russia","depth":8},{"id":143,"text":"with any Russians .","depth":7},{"id":144,"text":"According to his own account of the June 2016 meeting with Russian lawyer Natalia Veselnitskaya ,","depth":8},{"id":145,"text":"the two discussed adoption policy and the Magnitsky Act , a law","depth":10},{"id":146,"text":"that denies entrance to the U.S. to Russian human rights abusers .","depth":10},{"id":147,"text":"The law prompted Russian President Vladimir Putin to halt American adoption of Russian children .","depth":9},{"id":148,"text":"Trump Jr. told Fox News ' Sean Hannity on July 11","depth":8},{"id":149,"text":"that Veselnitskaya told \" a story about Russian adoption and how we could possibly help. \"","depth":8},{"id":150,"text":"Trump Jr. said","depth":7},{"id":151,"text":"he then quickly shut down the meeting","depth":8},{"id":152,"text":"because \" this wasn ' t a campaign talking point .","depth":9},{"id":153,"text":"This wasn ' t something","depth":12},{"id":154,"text":"we were -","depth":12},{"id":155,"text":"you know ,","depth":12},{"id":156,"text":"this was not something","depth":13},{"id":157,"text":"I was going to worry about at that stage .","depth":13},{"id":158,"text":"I mean ,","depth":11},{"id":159,"text":"we had a lot of bigger fish to fry . \"","depth":11},{"id":160,"text":"In the summer of 2016 , Trump Jr. made one other notable statement on Russian interference in the election .","depth":5},{"id":161,"text":"He didn ' t say anything about potential meetings ,","depth":6},{"id":162,"text":"but his reaction to the suggestion","depth":8},{"id":163,"text":"that the Russian government wanted to help his father ' s candidacy","depth":8},{"id":164,"text":"belied what he knew at the time .","depth":7},{"id":165,"text":"On July 22 , 2016 , WikiLeaks released nearly 20,000 Democratic National Committee emails .","depth":4},{"id":166,"text":"Two days later , on CNN ' s State of the Union , host Jake Tapper had this exchange with Trump Jr .","depth":6},{"id":167,"text":"CNN ' s Jake Tapper , July 24 , 2016 :","depth":7},{"id":168,"text":"`` Robby Mook , the campaign manager for Secretary of State Hillary Clinton -","depth":10},{"id":169,"text":"I asked him about the DNC leak .","depth":10},{"id":170,"text":"And he suggested","depth":10},{"id":171,"text":"that experts are saying","depth":11},{"id":172,"text":"that Russians were behind both the leak - the hacking of the DNC emails and their release .","depth":11},{"id":173,"text":"He seemed to be suggesting","depth":9},{"id":174,"text":"that this is part of a plot","depth":10},{"id":175,"text":"to help Donald Trump","depth":11},{"id":176,"text":"and hurt Hillary Clinton .","depth":11},{"id":177,"text":"Your response ? ''","depth":5},{"id":178,"text":"Trump Jr. :","depth":5},{"id":179,"text":"`` Well , it just goes to show you their exact moral compass .","depth":6},{"id":180,"text":"I mean ,","depth":9},{"id":181,"text":"they ' ll say anything","depth":10},{"id":182,"text":"to be able to win this .","depth":10},{"id":183,"text":"I mean ,","depth":9},{"id":184,"text":"this is time and time again , lie after lie .","depth":9},{"id":185,"text":"You notice","depth":10},{"id":186,"text":"he won ' t say ,","depth":11},{"id":187,"text":"well , I say this .","depth":11},{"id":188,"text":"We hear experts .","depth":12},{"id":189,"text":"You know ,","depth":13},{"id":190,"text":"his house cat at home once said","depth":14},{"id":191,"text":"that this is what ' s happening with the Russians .","depth":14},{"id":192,"text":"It ' s disgusting .","depth":12},{"id":193,"text":"It ' s so phony .","depth":12},{"id":194,"text":"I watched him bumble through the interview ,","depth":11},{"id":195,"text":"I was able to hear it on audio a little bit .","depth":11},{"id":196,"text":"I mean ,","depth":10},{"id":197,"text":"I can ' t think of bigger lies ,","depth":10},{"id":198,"text":"but that exactly goes to show you what the DNC and what the Clinton camp will do .","depth":10},{"id":199,"text":"They will lie","depth":11},{"id":200,"text":"and do anything","depth":12},{"id":201,"text":"to win . ''","depth":12},{"id":202,"text":"Of course , the U.S. intelligence community did later say , on Oct. 7 , 2016 ,","depth":6},{"id":203,"text":"that it is \" confident \"","depth":7},{"id":204,"text":"that hacks into the email systems of the Democratic Party and its officials were directed by the Russian government .","depth":7},{"id":205,"text":"And a Jan. 6 , 2017 , declassified intelligence report from the Office of the Director of National Intelligence said","depth":6},{"id":206,"text":"that Russian President Vladimir Putin had ordered the hacking ,","depth":7},{"id":207,"text":"designed to \" help President-elect Trump ' s election chances . \"","depth":7},{"id":208,"text":"To be clear ,","depth":7},{"id":209,"text":"there is nothing in the email chain or recent reporting","depth":8},{"id":210,"text":"to suggest","depth":9},{"id":211,"text":"Trump Jr. knew anything about Russian hacking of the DNC emails .","depth":9},{"id":212,"text":"But we do know","depth":7},{"id":213,"text":"that he had been told","depth":8},{"id":214,"text":"that the promise","depth":10},{"id":215,"text":"of incriminating information about Clinton","depth":10},{"id":216,"text":"was \" part of Russia and its government ' s support for Mr. Trump , \" in Goldstone ' s June 3 , 2016 , email .","depth":9},{"id":217,"text":"As for the elder Trump , the president was asked by ABC News ' Cecilia Vega at the conclusion of a Jan. 11 press conference , about a week before he was inaugurated :","depth":8},{"id":218,"text":"\" Did you or anyone in your campaign have any contact with Russia","depth":9},{"id":219,"text":"leading up to or during the campaign ? \"","depth":9},{"id":220,"text":"Trump ' s response , ABC News reported :","depth":9},{"id":221,"text":"\" No .","depth":10},{"id":222,"text":"Not at all. \"","depth":10},{"id":223,"text":"( See the 3-minute mark of the news segment . )","depth":8},{"id":224,"text":"Trump Jr. said in his July 11 Fox News interview","depth":8},{"id":225,"text":"that he didn ' t tell his father anything about the June 2016 meeting .","depth":8},{"id":226,"text":"President Trump also told Reuters on July 12","depth":8},{"id":227,"text":"that he \" didn ' t know \" about the meeting \" until a couple of days ago ,","depth":9},{"id":228,"text":"when I heard about this . \"","depth":9},{"id":229,"text":"Trump calls Donald Trump Jr. 's meeting with Russian lawyer 'opposition research","depth":7},{"id":230,"text":"'","depth":7},{"id":231,"text":"Did Donald Trump Jr. break any laws","depth":7},{"id":232,"text":"by seeking damaging information from Russia on Hillary Clinton ?","depth":7},{"id":233,"text":"Donald Trump Jr. 's Russian meeting :","depth":6},{"id":234,"text":"An unusual way","depth":7},{"id":235,"text":"of conducting political research","depth":7},{"id":236,"text":"Trump has deep ties to Putin-connected billionaire","depth":6},{"id":237,"text":"who offered dirt on Hillary","depth":6},{"id":238,"text":"Donald Trump Jr. on Russia meeting :","depth":6},{"id":239,"text":"'In retrospect , I probably would have done things a little differently '","depth":6}],"relations":[{"parent":479,"left":399,"right":478,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":399,"left":250,"right":398,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":250,"left":243,"right":249,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":243,"left":0,"right":242,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":242,"left":1,"right":241,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":241,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":249,"left":244,"right":248,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":244,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":248,"left":246,"right":247,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":246,"left":6,"right":245,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":245,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":247,"left":9,"right":10,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":398,"left":311,"right":397,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":311,"left":308,"right":310,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":308,"left":292,"right":307,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":292,"left":290,"right":291,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":290,"left":253,"right":289,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":253,"left":252,"right":14,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":252,"left":11,"right":251,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":251,"left":12,"right":13,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":289,"left":268,"right":288,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":268,"left":264,"right":267,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":264,"left":15,"right":263,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":263,"left":16,"right":262,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":262,"left":259,"right":261,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":259,"left":17,"right":258,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":258,"left":18,"right":257,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":257,"left":19,"right":256,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":256,"left":254,"right":255,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":254,"left":20,"right":21,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":255,"left":22,"right":23,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":261,"left":24,"right":260,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":260,"left":25,"right":26,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":267,"left":27,"right":266,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":266,"left":28,"right":265,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":265,"left":29,"right":30,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":288,"left":271,"right":287,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":271,"left":270,"right":34,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":270,"left":31,"right":269,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":269,"left":32,"right":33,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":287,"left":35,"right":286,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":286,"left":280,"right":285,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":280,"left":276,"right":279,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":276,"left":36,"right":275,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":275,"left":37,"right":274,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":274,"left":272,"right":273,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":272,"left":38,"right":39,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":273,"left":40,"right":41,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":279,"left":278,"right":45,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":278,"left":277,"right":44,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":277,"left":42,"right":43,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":285,"left":282,"right":284,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":282,"left":46,"right":281,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":281,"left":47,"right":48,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":284,"left":49,"right":283,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":283,"left":50,"right":51,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":291,"left":52,"right":53,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":307,"left":303,"right":306,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":303,"left":295,"right":302,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":295,"left":54,"right":294,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":294,"left":55,"right":293,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":293,"left":56,"right":57,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":302,"left":299,"right":301,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":299,"left":298,"right":62,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":298,"left":58,"right":297,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":297,"left":59,"right":296,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":296,"left":60,"right":61,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":301,"left":63,"right":300,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":300,"left":64,"right":65,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":306,"left":66,"right":305,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":305,"left":67,"right":304,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":304,"left":68,"right":69,"relation":"condition","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":310,"left":70,"right":309,"relation":"purpose","nucleari